divs: Sighting Detailswas outside smoking a cig, saw a bright light i saw a few mornings earlier. the light was in a different part of the sky. It also emitted two other objects that emitted colors that changed from red to yellow to white and green. also blinked. looked in the area around the object and observed two more lights that did the same. objects are still in the sky.
Summary: object brightened then dimmed,ejected lights that changed colors
